<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Business Consultant</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }
        .navbar {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }
        .card-body {
            color: white;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Career Guidance</a>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Business Consultant</h2>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5>Topics to Learn:</h5>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Business Strategy:</strong> SWOT Analysis, Competitive Analysis</li>
                    <li><strong>Market Research:</strong> Surveys, Focus Groups, Data Analysis</li>
                    <li><strong>Financial Modeling:</strong> Excel, Financial Forecasting</li>
                    <li><strong>Project Management:</strong> Agile, Scrum, Waterfall</li>
                    <li><strong>Client Management:</strong> Communication, Negotiation, Relationship Building</li>
                </ul>
                <h5>Skills Required:</h5>
                <ul>
                    <li>Problem-solving</li>
                    <li>Communication</li>
                    <li>Leadership</li>
                </ul>
                <h5>Career Path:</h5>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Junior Consultant:</strong> Assist in analyzing business problems.</li>
                    <li><strong>Senior Consultant:</strong> Lead consulting projects and teams.</li>
                    <li><strong>Partner:</strong> Oversee consulting firm operations.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
